er hot mikh zeyer lib. er kusht mikh, er kusht mikh, er haldzt un er kusht, er nemt mikh arum, er drukt mikh!

167
00:14:31,133 --> 00:14:36,814
un vos er hot nisht keyn mazl nebekh, er iz a kranker. er iz a kranker fun di krig.

168
00:14:37,967 --> 00:14:44,812
az ikh shvanger, az ikh bin nervez, vert dos kind oykh nervez? yo.

169
00:14:45,291 --> 00:14:52,761
azoy hot mir gezogt der dokter hot mir gezogt. nervez. m'hot tsugenumen man.

170
00:14:53,053 --> 00:15:01,079
bin ikh dokh gevorn meshuge, nervez, un ikh ho- un az ikh bin geven zeks monat, iz di nervn azoy arayn in im oykhet.

171
00:15:01,356 --> 00:15:08,842
m'hot im m'hot im opgenumen oyf a firer fun der politsey. hob ikh nisht getort geyn oyf der gas.

172
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:13,668
s'geven zibn in der fri, oyf zeks in der fri,

173
00:15:13,675 --> 00:15:19,322
ikh hob nisht getort oyf der gas, nor akhte hob ikh gemegt geyn. un dos kind geyt aroys,

174
00:15:19,767 --> 00:15:26,932
hob ikh gehe- hob gekmyeltshet, iz aroyfgekumen a shokhnte, zogt zi, "madam Goldbaum, vos iz geshen?

175
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:30,679
zog ikh, "dos kind geyt!" s'shoyn geven blut mit alem.

176
00:15:31,258 --> 00:15:38,036
hot zi mikh genumen, zi hot mikh gefirt arop oyf der gas, hot mikh gezetst in a in a re- in a ⟨skine⟩.

177
00:15:38,532 --> 00:15:45,259
un deriber iz geven a byuro tabak, a, veyst nisht a byuro tabak? a byuro tabak.

178
00:15:45,990 --> 00:15:53,662
u- un zi iz antlofn. mikh gelozt mit Zhakn, mit Alberto. un tsvey hob ikh avekgegebn.

179
00:15:54,293 --> 00:15:58,117
un un u- u- ikh blayb shteyn mit di kinder, ikh tsiter,

180
00:15:59,068 --> 00:16:07,916
ruft zikh on di fun byuro tabak, "kuk zikh kuk tsi s'zet nisht UNK madam. UNE BEBE. BEBE."

181
00:16:07,916 --> 00:16:14,098
hot zi gegebn a gey aron, hot oysgehakt a shaybl, zi redt mit im, iz shoyn do POLICE.

182
00:16:14,222 --> 00:16:19,330
zi hot geredt mitn shaybl un dortn gekumen dos POLICE. a ketshl mit POLICE.

183
00:16:20,584 --> 00:16:25,100
hobn zikh geze- do a do POLICE un do POLICE, a dokter oykhet.

184
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:33,200
m'nemt mikh aroys oyfn ke- oyf oyf dem oyf dem balans, ikh kon nisht shteyn.

185
00:16:33,595 --> 00:16:36,272
kh- kh- ikh fil az ikh s'geyt aroys dos kind.

186
00:16:36,497 --> 00:16:42,482
ikh shtey oy, hot a dokter dort zeyer heyst er zey aropgeyn un mikh hot er geleygt,

187
00:16:42,859 --> 00:16:46,430
shtekt arunter der hant, makht dos kepl shoyn in droysn.

188
00:16:46,673 --> 00:16:53,096
un biz ahin iz iz p- hot mir gen- -brengt a leyter, m'hot mikh arayngefirt.

189
00:16:53,862 --> 00:17:00,976
azoy. ikh hob gring kinder. a- a- ikh hob gemeynt s'vet nisht lebn.

190
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:08,705
hot er mir gezogt, "GARCON." far freyd hob ikh ongehoybn tsu veynen, makht er "PORQUOI PLURER? PORQUOI PLURER?"

191
00:17:09,589 --> 00:17:18,324
yo der der ikh vil a FILLE. ikh vil a meydele. "oh, s'a yingele! far di soldatn FRANCAIS."

192
00:17:19,005 --> 00:17:23,892
iz shoyn trakht ikh mir, vet zayn a yingele, ober ikh zol shoyn zayn nor tsurik in der heym.

193
00:17:23,933 --> 00:17:30,390
bin ikh gelign akhtsn tog in shpitol. dortn ligt men azoy, dortn ligt men azoy. akhtsn tog.

194
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:36,262
oyfn nayntstn tog geyt men arop fun bet un m'geyt arum un arum in ale betn.

195
00:17:36,572 --> 00:17:42,101
tsvontsikstn tog nemt men mikh aheym. bay ale kinder. yo yo yo.

196
00:17:42,107 --> 00:17:44,818
nor in Poyln nisht. in Poyln zibn tog.

197
00:17:47,997 --> 00:17:51,366
ikh hob gehat genug, ikh hob gehat genug oyf mayn lebn.

198
00:17:51,962 --> 00:17:54,808
ven di kinder zenen gekumen mit aykh,

199
00:17:54,493 --> 00:17:55,432
yo?

200
00:17:54,966 --> 00:17:57,440
vu ahin zent ets gegangen?

201
00:17:58,054 --> 00:17:59,718
vi lang zenen geve-

202
00:17:58,071 --> 00:18:02,925
no, vu hin zent ets gegangen mit di kinder?

203
00:18:02,425 --> 00:18:09,792
der yene fun dort hot dokh mir opgegebn di shtub. bin ikh arayngeganen in shtub arayn.

204
00:18:10,322 --> 00:18:15,953
yo, o tsehakt, tsebrokt! ikh hob nisht ge- di vant iz geven tseshpoltn nor aribertsufaln.

205
00:18:16,195 --> 00:18:19,462
un ayere zakhn zenen geven in- ineveynik?

206
00:18:20,295 --> 00:18:24,339
keyn pitsele nisht. keyn ⟨dzharke⟩ mist iz gevezn.

207
00:18:24,852 --> 00:18:31,446
er hot gemakht a tel fun di shtub hot er gemakht. vos hob ikh gekont tun?

208
00:18:27,248 --> 00:18:34,531
dos mebl oykhet nisht? nor dos mebl? ayer mebl?

209
00:18:33,150 --> 00:18:36,945
ales tsugenumen, alts tsugenumen, alts alts.

210
00:18:37,812 --> 00:18:45,314
ikh bin arayn a a a marokhe zey hobn mir gegebn valizke mit zakhn, mit ontuekhts. un farn meydl oykhet.

211
00:18:45,574 --> 00:18:48,439
bin bay di yinglekh oykhet, shikh, mit ale.

212
00:18:48,439 --> 00:18:52,185
bin ikh arayn mit dem, dos hob ikh gehat, hot men bald arayngeshtelt,

213
00:18:52,185 --> 00:18:55,119
nisht geven keyn plakat, s'gor nisht gevezn.

214
00:18:56,104 --> 00:19:05,295
hot er hot er mir bald arayngeshtelt a shenkl, Leon Fridman, ikh hob arayngehongen di ale zakhn,

215
00:19:05,942 --> 00:19:12,753
un a bet hot er gebrengt fun di kazarme, yo, er hot getun guts far mir!

216
00:19:13,198 --> 00:19:22,088
un mit a goyishe ⟨ASSIETTE⟩, mit kartofles, di mit pudles esnvarg.

217
00:19:22,088 --> 00:19:26,659
nor di pudles hobn di kinder gegesn, ikh nisht, ikh hob nisht getort esn.

218
00:19:27,407 --> 00:19:30,691
un ikh ikh bin shoyn geblibn azoy.

219
00:19:30,816 --> 00:19:33,881
vi alt zenen geven di kinder in dem moment?

220
00:19:33,853 --> 00:19:35,703
ikh hob zey aroysgenumen?

221
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:36,277
yo.

222
00:19:36,351 --> 00:19:46,132
Lazer Suzan iz shoyn alt geven fu- zekhtsn yor. Ab iz alt gevezn fuftsn fertsn yor, fertsn.

223
00:19:46,577 --> 00:20:00,206
Zhak iz geven nayn yor. fertsn, dray yor nokh im, fertsn, dray yor nokh Albertn.

224
00:20:00,887 --> 00:20:09,893
un Leon iz gevezn zeks yor. Lazer iz alt gevezn dray yor.

225
00:20:11,991 --> 00:20:16,726
vi lang zent ir geblibn lebn dortn in shtub?

226
00:20:17,188 --> 00:20:27,139
nisht lang. ikh bin aroys fun di shtub hob ikh far- far- farmakht, far⟨UNK⟩, hob ikh genumen shlisl gelt.

227
00:20:28,258 --> 00:20:31,846
dortn farkoyft men nisht. far shlisl-gelt.

228
00:20:32,815 --> 00:20:39,289
dernokh dem hot er mikh arumgezukht, er hot gevolt dos gelt, a- az di shtub iz tsebrokhn.

229
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:44,000
farrakhtet, tsu hobn a shtub. un m'hot ayngeleygt di shtub, azoy.

230
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:49,109
in di UNK ge- ge- gornisht geven keyn shtubn. zey hobn ale shtubn tsebrokhn.

231
00:20:51,343 --> 00:20:55,420
ven hot ir zikh bakent mitn tsveytn man?

232
00:20:56,220 --> 00:21:01,912
in di in di bay Rotshildn in di di in vu m- vu geshlofn.

233
00:21:01,873 --> 00:21:03,588
vi hot er geheysn?

234
00:21:03,561 --> 00:21:09,191
Kha- Shloyme. Shloyme hot er geheysn a Hershkop.

235
00:21:10,598 --> 00:21:13,376
vu ahin zent ir geforn mit im?

236
00:21:14,142 --> 00:21:16,602
er iz bald avekgeforn.

237
00:21:15,525 --> 00:21:16,751
vu hin?

238
00:21:16,602 --> 00:21:20,835
keyn Bolivye. di shvester hot im aribergenumen, bald bald.

239
00:21:21,263 --> 00:21:26,504
un un tsu mir hot er gezogt, "ikh vel zayn a tate tsu di kinder."

240
00:21:26,629 --> 00:21:32,397
"oy," zog ikh, "no, vos darft ir un a tate? nemt aykh a meydl, nemt aykh a yunge froy!"

241
00:21:32,397 --> 00:21:38,641
zog ikh, ikh hob finef kinder, zogt er, er vet zayn a tate tsu di kinder. "ikh hob lib kinder."

242
00:21:38,641 --> 00:21:43,531
er hot nisht lib gehat di kinder. er hot mikh er hot mikh ahin genart.

243
00:21:44,297 --> 00:21:50,518
mir veln zikh do opshteln un bald vet ir dertseyln vayter. m'vet zikh opshteln do.

244
00:21:50,389 --> 00:21:51,297
yo?

245
00:21:50,743 --> 00:21:51,280
yo.

